title: Synth World (10 Original Synthwave Songs)
longDescription:
Take a nostalgic trip back to the 1980s with Synth World. 10 Unique synthwave songs inspired by everything from Stranger Things to droids taking over a cyberpunk city. Call it synthwave, outrun, retrowave or vaporwave, it's time to take a neon filled drive through Synth World.


Demo Preview
